2Fi.insider.com%2F5ec72d9eaee6a807f1578305%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDalgona%20coffee%20inspired%20TikTok.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPopular%20food%20trends%20on%20TikTok%20right%20now%20are%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20twists%20on%20familiar%20dishes.%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fanneta-konstantinides%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20lifestyle%20editor%20at%20Insider%20who%20reports%20on%20TikTok%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20definitely%20seeing%20miniature%20as%20a%20huge%20trend%20for%20these%20TikTok%20pieces%2C%20and%20influencers%20have%20said%20the%20same%20to%20me%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20this%20article's%20publication%2C%20videos%20with%20the%20hashtag%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fminitutorials%3Fsource%3Dh5_t%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fminitutorials%3Fsource%253Dh5_t%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1590163055525000%26amp%3Busg%3DAFQjCNHc4XRpM67aIu-w2QNSLOPaSWSlDg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23MiniTutorials%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%202%20billion%20combined%20views.%20A%20particularly%20popular%20mini%20food%20idea%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fpancakecereal%3Fsource%3Dh5_t%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fpancakecereal%3Fsource%253Dh5_t%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1590163055524000%26amp%3Busg%3DAFQjCNGJVpY5tMztFr4WDD4K796ZOsoq_A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23PancakeCereal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20985%20million%20combined%20views%20and%20has%20inspired%20scores%20of%20spinoffs%2C%20including%20cookie%20cereal%20and%20donut%20cereal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKonstantinides%20believes%20the%20trend%20works%20because%20it's%20cute%20but%20also%20reflects%20nostalgia%20and%20our%20current%20mood.%20%26quot%3BCookies%2C%20pancakes%2C%20and%20cereal%20are%20all%20things%20we%20had%20as%20kids%20when%20we%20were%20living%20at%20home%20with%20our%20parents%2C%20and%20now%20we're%20making%20them%20for%20ourselves%20while%20in%20quarantine.%20I%20think%20it%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20our%20childhood%20a%20bit%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20us%20who%20can't%20be%20with%20our%20parents%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalgona%20coffee%2C%20the%20beautiful%20whipped%20beverage%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen_us%2Farticle%2Fpkenb8%2Fa-dive-into-the-disputed-history-of-dalgona-coffee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20origins%20in%20various%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20India%2C%20Greece%2C%20and%20Libya%2C%20and%20was%20popularized%20by%20Korean%20YouTubers%20in%20early%202020%2C%20is%20another%20one%20that%20comes%20up%20again%20and%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20truly%20perfect%20for%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Konstantinides.%20%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20impressive%20in%20photos%20and%20it%20needs%20a%20bit%20of%20time%20to%20make%2C%20which%20we%20all%20have%20right%20now!%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20can%20so%20easily%20tweak%20the%20recipe%20and%20make%20so%20many%20kinds%20of%20whips%2C%20even%20vegan%2C%20has%20made%20it%20very%20accessible.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhile%20the%20above%20trends%20can%20take%20some%20time%20to%20master%2C%20users%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20cut%20corners%20in%20the%20kitchen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuch%20of%20the%20current%20food%20and%20drink%20content%20on%20TikTok%20is%20focused%20around%20hacks...there's%20a%20lot%20of%20content%20right%20now%20that's%20about%20simplicity%20and%20using%20ingredients%20that%20you%20already%20have%20in%20your%20home%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20really%20elaborate%20recipe%20or%20cooking%20tutorial%20like%20you'll%20see%20on%20YouTube%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mary%20Keane-Dawson%2C%20group%20CEO%20of%20influencer%20marketing%20platform%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftakumi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETakumi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20advises%20clients%20on%20food%20and%20drink%20content%20strategy%20on%20TikTok.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExamples%20include%20demos%20on%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40flakeysalt%2Fvideo%2F6823017446882987269%3Fsource%3Dh5_t%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20a%20large%20and%20unwieldy%20watermelon%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20freeze%20herbs%20and%20olive%20oil%20in%20an%20ice%20cube%20tray%20for%20easy%20storage%20and%20meal%20prep.%20Many%20of%20these%20tips%20and%20tricks%20have%20floated%20around%20the%20Internet%20for%20years%2C%20but%20TikTok%2C%20with%20its%2060-second%20clip%20limit%20and%20tools%20to%20easily%20add%20text%2C%20voiceovers%2C%20and%20other%20effects%2C%20lends%20itself%20perfectly%20to%20the%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20telling%20that%20even%20when%20users%20are%20stuck%20at%20home%20and%20theoretically%20have%20all%20the%20time%20in%20the%20world%2C%20they%20still%20find%20comfort%20in%20optimizing%20that%20time%20and%20making%20their%20lives%20easier.%20Another%20explanation%20is%20that%20as%20stay-at-home%20orders%20drag%20on%2C%20the%20initial%20shiny%20excitement%20of%20creating%20complex%20meals%20wears%20away%20and%20people%20just%20want%20to%20stay%20fed%20with%20little%20effort.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20can't%20predict%20the%20exact%20recipes%20that%20will%20become%20popular%20in%20upcoming%20months%2C%20we're%20guessing%20that%20aesthetics%2C%20nostalgia%2C%20and%20hacks%20will%20remain%20relevant%20themes%20in%20home%20kitchens%20everywhere%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20try%20some%20of%20the%20best%20TikTok%20food%20trends%2C%20we've%20included%20recipes%2C%20tips%2C%20and%20recommended%20products%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20make%203%20of%20the%20best%20TikTok%20food%20trends%20at%20home%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDalgona%20coffee%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dalgona%20coffee%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ec6ed981918246d6c4ddc45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20you%20need%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1%20tbsp%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-instant-coffees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstant%20coffee%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20your%20choice%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1%20tbsp%20sugar%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1%20tbsp%20hot%20water%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1%20cup%20milk%20of%20your%20choice%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-hand-mixer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehand%20mixer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-milk-frother%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20frother%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-whisk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhisk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESteps%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMix%20coffee%2C%20sugar%2C%