3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20City%20Slip%20and%20the%20RS02%20sneakers%20fit%20true%20to%20size%2C%20but%20between%20the%20wider%20rounded%20toe%20boxes%20and%20the%20available%20half%20sizes%2C%20they%20both%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20more%20comfortable%20than%20previous%20Rothy's%20styles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wear%20a%20full%20size%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20new%20half%20sizes%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20in%20between%20sizes%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20deciding%20to%20order%20a%20half%20size%20up%20or%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20both%20styles%20are%20unisex%2C%20they%20are%20labeled%20with%20men's%20and%20women's%20sizing.%20Order%20your%20true%20size%20for%20a%20good%20fit%20with%20or%20without%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20Consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20nothing%20negative%20to%20say%20about%20Rothy's%20original%20releases%20for%20men%20and%20I'm%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20they've%20only%20made%20improvements%20since%20then.%20With%20the%20new%20styles%20ranging%20from%20%24139%20to%20%24149%2C%20they're%20more%20affordable%20than%20both%20of%20the%20other%20men's%20styles.%20With%20half%20sizes%20available%2C%20you'll%20also%20have%20an%20easier%20time%20getting%20the%20proper%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20more%20traditional%20leather%20or%20canvas%20sneakers%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20shop%20elsewhere%2C%20but%20with%20Rothy's%20active%20approach%20to%20sustainability%2C%20that's%20a%20given.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224030%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rothy's%20sneakers%20review%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63335c2b302812001934af5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20since%20Rothy's%20first%20made%20shoes%20for%20men%20and%20this%20second%20installment%20of%20men's%20releases%20proves%20that%20the%20brand%20can%20do%20no%20wrong.%20Both%20the%20City%20Slip%20and%20RS02%20sneakers%20are%20comfortable%2C%20casual%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20care%20for.%20Even%20if%20sustainability%20isn't%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20you%2C%20having%20sneakers%20that%20are%20truly%20machine%20washable%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20caring%20for%20your%20shoes%20and%20maintaining%20their%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Frothys-mens-sneakers-review-second-release%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633356fd302812001934ad83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Frothys-mens-sneakers-review-second-release%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20unisex%20style%20and%20extended%20half%20sizes%2C%20the%20City%20Slip%20and%20RS02%20Sneakers%20are%20some%20of%20Rothy's%20most%20comfortable%20shoes%20to%20date.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aismael%40businessinsider.com%20(Amir%20Ismael)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Frothys-mens-sneakers-review-second-release%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22These%20crunchy%2C%20flavorful%2C%20and%20nutritious%20snacks%20are%20surprisingly%20made%20from%20roasted%20fava%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20we%20absolutely%20love%20them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EL