a-boom-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5deecae5fd9db21f12604705%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbada-bean-bada-boom-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20I%20hate%20cooked%20broad%20beans%2C%20I%20love%20Bada%20Bean%20Bada%20Boom%20snacks%2C%20a%20fun%2C%20crunchy%2C%20and%20flavorful%20alternative%20to%20boring%20snacks%20like%20almonds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cchen%40insider.com%20(Connie%20Chen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbada-bean-bada-boom-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Investing%20veteran%20George%20Noble%20says%20the%20market%20is%20ignoring%20a%20warning%20flashing%20in%20oil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crude%20oil%20futures%20price%20screen%20flashing%20a%20decline.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8b8063fecbb42897a28ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENYSE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGeorge%20Noble%20says%20the%20market%20is%20too%20complacent%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20oil.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20physical%20oil%20is%20pricing%20the%20war%20correctly%2C%20while%20oil%20futures%20are%20not.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20views%20energy%20stocks%20as%20the%20most%20strategic%20trade%20to%20guard%20against%20Iran-driven%20losses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20futures%20are%20trading%20around%20%24100%20a%20barrel%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20investors%20assess%20the%20fragile%20state%20of%20the%20US-Iran%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20Wall%20Street%20veteran%20George%20Noble%20thinks%20the%20market%20is%20still%20not%20bearish%20enough%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-rise-ahead-us-iran-peace-talks-in-pakistan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat's%20happening%20in%20crude%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoble%2C%20the%20former%20director%20of%20the%20Fidelity%20Overseas%20Fund%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20multiple%20hedge%20funds%2C%20said%20that%20he%20sees%20the%20Iran%20war%20exposing%20a%20dangerous%20disconnect%20between%20physical%20and%20%26quot%3Bpaper%26quot%3B%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20physical%20market%20is%20pricing%20a%20war.%20The%20paper%20market%20is%20pricing%20a%20peace%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgnoble79%2Fstatus%2F2046603397533511746%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20them%20is%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spot%20price%20of%20Brent%20crude%20surged%20above%20%24140%20a%20barrel%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20highest%20level%20since%20the%202008%20crisis.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Brent%20futures%20peaked%20just%20below%20%24120%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20March%20shortly%20after%20the%20war%20broke%20out.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoble%20thinks%20the%20physical%20oil%20market%20is%20priced%20correctly%20because%20it%20reflects%20supply%20constraints%20in%20real%20time.%20Paper%20oil%2C%20referring%20to%20financial%20instruments%20such%20as%20futures%2C%20is%20driven%20by%20forecasts%2C%20beliefs%2C%20and%20narratives%20that%20can%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20incorrect.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoble%20sees%20the%20risk%20in%20physical%20oil%20markets%20is%20anything%20but%20hypothetical.%20With%20the%20state%20of%20shipping%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20still%20uncertain%2C%20oil%20flows%20remain%20halted%2C%20and%20energy%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20region%20is%20still%20damaged.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20two%20completely%20different%20wars%20being%20fought%20at%20the%20same%20time%20-%20one%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20has%20already%20solved%2C%20and%20one%20it%20cannot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20paper%20oil%20prices%20are%20trading%20like%20this%20distinction%20doesn't%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20closure%20is%20impacting%20industries%20beyond%20oil%2C%20including%20fertilizer%2C%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-inflation-oil-prices-fertilizer-farmers-iran-war-shipping-hormuz-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewide-ranging%20implications%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20agriculture%2C%20and%20helium%2C%20which%20could%20have%20knock-on%20effects%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-supply-chains-iran-war-ai-helium-food-inflation-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedicine%20and%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20commodities%20can%20be%20moved%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20Noble%20noted%20that%20these%20solutions%20don't%20extend%20to%20physical%20oil%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20easy%20fix%20for%20the%20extreme%20disruption%20to%20global%20energy%20flows.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20disconnect%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20oil%20market%20continuing%20to%20intensify%20and%20no%20clear%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20sight%2C%20Noble%20maintains%20that%20investors%20should%20be%20prioritizing%20the%20energy%20trade%2C%20a%20playbook%20that%20other%20finance%20pros%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-top-stock-picks-energy-trump-war-iran-markets-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20recommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20means%20of%20guarding%20against%20losses%20stemming%20from%20the%20economic%20fallout.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BEnergy%20stocks%20remain%20the%20most%20asymmetric%20trade%20in%20this%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Noble%20aded.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20paper%20catches%20up%20to%20physical%20(and%2045%20years%20of%20experience%20tells%20me%20it%20always%20does)%20the%20repricing%20will%20be%20violent%26quot%3B.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-noble-warns-oil-markets-prices-futures-commodities-iran-shipping-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e8cc243fecbb42897a28fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-noble-warns-oil-markets-prices-futures-commodities-iran-shipping-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22George%20Noble%20highlights%20the%20risk%20in%20oil%20markets%20amid%20Iran%20war%20tensions%2C%20warning%20investors%20about%20the%20disconnect%20between%20physical%20oil%20and%20oil%20futures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorge-noble-warns-oil-markets-prices-futures-commodities-iran-shipping-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd's%20first-ever%20sneakers%20are%20%24229%2C%20but%20worth%20every%20penny%20if%20you%20care%20about%20comfort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221661%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%20Glider%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd3025e021b4c13311f00e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFounded%20by%20former%20Adidas%20and%20New%20Balance%20designer%20Justin%20Schneider%2C%C2%A0%