rvice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwolfandshepherd.com%252Fcollections%252Fglider-sneaker%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%20Glider%20Sneaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20features%20soft%2C%20premium%20Italian%20leather%20on%20the%20exterior%20and%20interior%20of%20the%20upper%20and%20a%20classic%20rubber%20cup%20sole.%20While%20its%20minimal%20aesthetic%20is%20similar%20to%20plenty%20of%20other%20sneakers%20available%20(some%20that%20you%20might%20already%20own)%2C%20the%20ultra-plush%20memory%20foam%20insole%20is%20what%20separates%20it%20from%20the%20bunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%20glider%20sneaker%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd2fd0e021b4c15ab2c2cf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Glider%20Sneaker%20is%20available%20in%20midnight%2C%20white%2C%20and%20black%20(pictured%20left%20to%20right)%20for%20%24225%20each%20and%20black%20patent%20leather%20(pictured%20below)%20for%20%24245.%3Cp%3EWolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20wear%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20former%20Syracuse%20runner%20Juris%20Silenieks%20setting%20the%20world%20record%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-57114-20%26h%3Dda8b09c6fe5bd67f38a25d1ad7a62ae714d191f8baecdce148aaf12ce4eee3c7%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42455%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fwolf-and-shepherd-glider-sneaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwolfandshepherd.com%252Fblogs%252Fthe-den%252Fworld-record%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20fastest%20half-marathon%20ran%20in%20its%20dress%20shoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20founder%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwolf-and-shepherd-toro-collection-review-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustin%20Schneider%20participating%20in%20the%202018%20Running%20of%20the%20Bulls%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Spain%2C%20Wolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%20has%20always%20gone%20to%20extreme%20measures%20to%20emphasize%20just%20how%20well%20the%20shoes%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20release%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-57114-20%26h%3Ddf0b510baeab5d78dc0d4c078fac8e879355177ad4dccd017f37ffd30ba2e251%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42455%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fwolf-and-shepherd-glider-sneaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwolfandshepherd.com%252Fcollections%252Fglider-sneaker%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlider%20Sneaker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20put%20them%20to%20the%20test%20alongside%20Schneider%20with%20an%20admittedly%20less%20intense%2C%20but%20still%20undeniably%20physical%20sport%3A%20squash.%20I%20laced%20them%20up%20and%20hit%20the%20squash%20court%20for%20some%20lessons%20and%20a%20few%20games%2C%20and%20I%20would%20have%20never%20imagined%20being%20able%20to%20perform%20so%20well%20in%20a%20shoe%20that%20wasn't%20specifically%20designed%20for%20sport.%20In%20the%20few%20hours%20we%20played%2C%20which%20consisted%20of%20short%20sprints%20and%20sharp%20cuts%20while%20running%20around%20the%20court%2C%20I%20broke%20a%20full%20sweat%20and%20my%20feet%20didn't%20hurt%20even%20the%20slightest%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20average%20person%20won't%20spend%20much%20time%20specifically%20playing%20sports%20in%20the%20Glider%20Sneaker%2C%20I%20also%20wore%20them%20like%20a%20normal%20person.%20My%20first%20impression%20of%20the%20leather%20pair%20was%20that%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20comfortable%20than%20the%20patent%20leather%20pair%20I%20played%20squash%20in.%20It%20didn't%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20because%20the%20leather%20is%20more%20supple%20and%20I%20suspect%20it'll%20get%20even%20better%20as%20I%20wear%20them%20more.%20Each%20step%20felt%20great%20throughout%20an%20entire%20day%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insole%20features%20three%20layers%20of%20memory%20foam%20with%20one%20layer%20extending%20to%20the%20arch%20of%20your%20foot.%20With%20added%20arch%20support%20%E2%80%94%20something%20most%20dress%20sneakers%20skip%20out%20on%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Glider%20Sneaker%20is%20more%20than%20adequate%20for%20meeting%20the%20needs%20of%20city%20goers%20and%20commuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%20Podium%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd33b8b021b4c258a23859a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221817%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20black%20patent%20leather%20Glider%20Sneaker%20released%20as%20part%20of%20the%20three-shoe%20Podium%20Collection.%20Click%20here%20to%20shop%20the%20full%20collection.%3Cp%3EWolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Glider%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-57114-20%26h%3Df42871978646dedc1ae6f0b883b1e3893a5b6ef788c4fb6b81cb85b9f7bd214b%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42455%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fwolf-and-shepherd-glider-sneaker-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwolfandshepherd.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWolf%20%26amp%3B%20Shepherd%3C%2Fa%3