3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESweaters%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERent%20the%20Runway%20has%20a%20ton%20of%20sweaters%20in%20their%20catalog.%20I%20generally%20have%20avoided%20them%20because%2C%20to%20me%2C%20they're%20not%20as%20special%20as%20the%20dresses%2C%20pants%2C%20blazers%2C%20and%20the%20like.%20But%20now%20that%20I'm%20working%20from%20home%2C%20a%20nice%20sweater%20is%20a%20perfect%20piece%20to%20lounge%20around%20in.%20Go%20for%20something%20that%20looks%20soft%20and%20luxurious%20and%20be%20sure%20to%20read%20the%20reviews.%20A%20scratchy%20sweater%20is%20only%20worth%20it%20if%20you%20can%20sport%20it%20for%20compliments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ETees%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20never%20thought%20to%20look%20on%20RTR%20for%20T-shirts%20until%20I%20was%20browsing%20for%20some%20WFH%20pieces%20and%20I%20stumbled%20across%20a%20cute%20polo.%20It%20is%20truly%20just%20a%20T-shirt%20with%20a%20collar%2C%20but%20hey%2C%20at%20least%20I'm%20making%20use%20of%20my%20subscription.%20If%20you%20search%20%26quot%3BT-shirt%26quot%3B%20you'll%20be%20served%20some%20loungy%20dresses%2C%20button-ups%2C%20and%20even%20silk%20pajama%20shirts.%20If%20it%20looks%20like%20you%20can%20lounge%20in%20it%2C%20you%20probably%20can%20lounge%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESweatpants%20and%20leggings%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sweatpant%20options%20are%20limited%2C%20but%20you'll%20never%20feel%20as%20fancy%20as%20you%20do%20lounging%20in%20sweats%20that%20cost%20more%20than%20the%20subscription%20itself.%20Search%20%26quot%3Bleggings%26quot%3B%20and%20you'll%20have%20a%20full%20page%20of%20items%20to%20choose%20from.%20When%20you're%20working%20from%20home%2C%20you%20can%20be%20anyone%20you%20want%2C%20like%20someone%20who%20wears%20suede%2C%20metallic%2C%20leopard%2C%20or%20camo%20leggings.%20The%20list%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22RTR%20work%20from%20home%20outfit%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6b981f235c184a3