C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fuseful-products-that-make-quarantine-easier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erethinking%20the%20atmosphere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0their%20home%20provides.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20we're%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20and%20surrounded%20by%20the%20same%20four%20walls%20all%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20it's%20natural%20to%20want%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-simple-things-to-make-home-cozy-social-distancing-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupgrade%20your%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20as%20we%20continue%20managing%20the%20coldest%20season%20of%20the%20year%2C%20having%20a%20warm%2C%20inviting%2C%20and%20calm%20home%20may%20help%20you%20get%20through%20the%20darkest%20days%20(literally).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20keyword%20to%20focus%20on%20here%20is%20'calm'%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20time%20where%20everything%20around%20us%20feels%20uncertain%2C%20this%20becomes%20a%20crucial%20theme%20to%20carry%20throughout%20every%20room.%20New%20York%20City-based%20clinical%20psychologist%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Ftherapists%2Fgladys-frankel-new-york-ny%2F77431%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gladys%20Frankel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ph.D.%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20in%20this%20unique%20environment%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-coronavirus-covid19-pandemic-stress-is-doing-to-your-brain-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunusual%20stressors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20need%20our%20space%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20oasis%2C%20a%20vacation%2C%20and%20a%20spa%20for%20our%20mind%20and%20body.%20This%20improves%20our%20mental%20health%2C%20fights%20anxiety%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fself-care-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egives%20us%20a%20kind%20of%20comfort%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0we%20may%20not%20currently%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20from%20our%20friends%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20create%20more%20calm%20in%20your%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElliot%20March%2C%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmawd.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%20and%20White%20Design%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20London%2C%20told%20Insider%20the%20first%20step%20to%20make%20a%20space%20more%20calming%20is%20to%20go%20through%20a%20soul-searching%20exercise%20and%20define%20what%20'calm'%20means%20to%20you%2C%20your%20family%2C%20your%20partner%2C%20or%20your%20roommate.%20Everyone%20values%20different%20things%20%E2%80%94%20some%20need%20a%20clutter-free%20area%20while%20others%20value%20framed%20photos%20of%20people%20they%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditional%20and%20cozy%20may%20feel%20soothing%20for%20one%20person%2C%20while%20minimalist%20and%20clean%20could%20work%20for%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20March%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20right%20or%20wrong%2C%20and%20these%20moods%20can%2C%20and%20should%2C%20be%20layered%20to%20add%20authenticity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20decide%20what%20kind%20of%20changes%20feel%20realistic%20to%20make.%20In%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20you'd%20have%20a%20spacious%20house%20with%20different%20rooms%20to%20work%20and%20relax%20in%2C%20and%20an%20extensive%20budget%20(with%20endless%20mental%20bandwidth)%20to%20redesign%20whatever%20room%20isn't%20delivering%20the%20calm%20vibes%20you%20seek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20many%20of%20us%20live%20in%20small%20spaces%20or%20without%20the%20budget%20to%20do%20a%20full%20(or%20even%20partial)%20overhaul.%20That's%20why%20interior%20designer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lisaqueendesign.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELisa%20Queen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggests%20starting%20with%20one%20corner%20and%20allowing%20it%20to%20embrace%20the%20calmness%20and%20comfort%20you%20desire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20might%20be%20a%20neglected%20corner%2C%20niche%2C%20or%20room%20in%20your%20home%20that%20would%20make%20the%20perfect%20spot%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-to-meditate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeditation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reading%2C%20or%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Queen%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOftentimes%2C%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20or%20a%20living%20room%20has%20seldom-used%20space%20that%20can%20be%20transformed%20into%20a%20grounding%20reprieve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20turning%20the%20broom%20closet%20into%20your%20cozy%20corner%20or%20overhauling%20your%20entire%20bedroom%20to%20help%20lower%20your%20anxiety%2C%20the%20approach%20is%20the%20same%3A%20Add%20a%20few%20elements%20that%20help%20you%20unwind%20like%20on%20an%20oversized%20chair%2C%20a%20chunky%20throw%20blanket%2C%20a%20soft%20pillow%2C%20a%20spot%20for%20your%20tea%20(or%20wine)%2C%20mood%20lighting%2C%20or%20even%20just%20a%20candle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpping%20the%20calm-factor%20of%20your%20space%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20expensive%2C%20either%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20it%20can%20actually%20be%20free.%20Strategically-chosen%20sm