th_Benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6392855%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebergamot%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20well%20known%20to%20relieve%20stress%20and%20anxiety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20goods%20to%20calm%20your%20space%20with%20scent%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESeparate%20your%20work%20and%20life%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222662%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20working%20desk%20small%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5febb3d3b7ab82001943e844%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20us%20learned%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwork-from-home-essentials-hub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20remotely%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20and%20are%20now%20carrying%20that%20knowledge%20into%202021.%20If%20you%20haven't%20already%2C%20it's%20vital%20to%20separate%20your%20workspace%20from%20your%20living%20space%20to%20offer%20your%20mind%20a%20much-needed%20break%20from%20being%20'on'%2024%2F7%2C%20interior%20designer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eddiezaratsian.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEddie%20Zaratsian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20least%2C%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20pack%20up%20'work'%20each%20day%20so%20it's%20out%20of%20sight%20and%20thus%2C%20out%20of%20mind.%20As%20Culver%20City%2C%20California-based%20marriage%20and%20family%20therapist%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ambertrueblood.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmber%20Trueblood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20explained%20to%20Insider%2C%20our%20senses%20are%20often%20bombarded%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20and%20when%20we%20notice%20a%20pile%20of%20work%20papers%20or%20our%20open%20laptop%20late%20at%20night%2C%20it%20can%20make%20us%20feel%20overwhelmed%20and%20may%20even%20encourage%20us%20to%20finish%20a%20little%20more%20work%20rather%20than%20unwinding%20and%20focusing%20on%20being%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20live%20in%20a%20smaller%20apartment%20and%20typically%20work%20from%20your%20kitchen%20counter%2C%20make%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20physically%20put%20your%20work%20laptop%20away%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20day%2C%20even%20if%20that's%20just%20in%20a%20neat%20pile%20under%20the%20coffee%20table.%20(And%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20your%20shoulders%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20back%2C%20try%20and%20make%20your%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-work-from-home-tech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkspace%20as%20ergonomic%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20possible.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20an%20unused%20room%20in%20your%20house%20or%20even%20a%20corner%20that%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-desk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esqueeze%20a%20desk%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%2C%20convert%20it%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fuseful-desk-accessories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededicated%20work%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Etsy%20has%20endless%20inventive%20options%20for%20floating%20murphy%20desks%20that%20you%20can%20fold%20out%20to%20work%20on%20and%20latch%20flat%20against%20the%20wall%20when%20you%20need%20that%20space%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaratsian%20added%20that%20not%20only%20will%20it%20help%20you%20feel%20calmer%20to%20have%20spots%20where%20you%20check%20email%20and%20places%20where%20you%20don't%2C%20but%20it'll%20improve%20your%20productivity%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwork-from-home-essentials-hub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20guide%20to%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20work%20from%20home%2C%20according%20to%20product%20reviewers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20items%20to%20keep%20work%20contained%20and%20comfortable%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECreate%20symmetry%20and%20repetition%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexandra%20Gater%20apartment%20bedroom%205%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5febb0d2b7ab82001943e835%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Kolyn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20object%20that%20is%20repetitive%20can%20facilitate%20calm%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Frankel%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20stimuli%20are%20repeated%2C%20neural%20activity%20is%20reduced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20same%20thinking%20for%20symmetry%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3130383%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escience%20has%20long%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20are%20drawn%20too%20in%20faces%2C%20images%2C%20and%20objects.%20Symmetry%20indicates%20purpose%20and%20intent%2C%20March%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20cheapest%20changes%20since%20it%20usually%20only%20involves%20re-arranging%20items%20you%20already%20own.%20Start%20in%20the%20rooms%20you%20spend%20the%20most%20time%20relaxing%20in%20and%20choose%20a%20center%20point%20you%20look%20at%20when%20you%20walk%20in%20or%20when%20you're%20sitting%20in%20your%20favorite%20spot.%20Work%20outward%20from%20the%20middle%2C%20placing%20objects%20on%20either%20side%20and%20designing%20for%20a%20mirror%20image.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20work%20with%20matching%20pieces%20as%20decorative%20items%2C%20like%20bookends%20or%20vases%2C%20and%20incorporate%20circular%20shapes%20to%20keep%20the%20mind%20relaxed.%20An%20easy%20way%20to%20achieve%20Dr.%20Frankel's%20calming%20repetition%20is%20by%20pulling%20up%20the%20now-classic%20fireplace%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%2FZY3J3Y_OU0w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20your%20TV%20to%20unwind%20(or%20even%20a%20real%20fireplace%20if%20you%20have%20one).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20to%20create%20symmetry%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELower%20your%20lighting%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22girl%20string%20lights%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5febb844a644880018193c10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222562%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECounter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20natural%20elements%2C%20light%20%E2%80%94%20both%20natural%20and%20human-made%20%E2%80%94%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20factors%20in%20helping%20your%20home%20to%20feel%20at%20ease%2C%20according%20to%20interior%20designer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nunnerley.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESandra%20Nunnerley%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe's%20right%3A%20Researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%20Scarborough%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.utoronto.ca%2Fmedia-releases%2Feducation%2Fnew-research-shows-the-way-a-room-is-lit-can-affect-the-way-you-make-decisions%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dwebsite%26utm_source%3Darchdaily.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20human%20emotion%2C%20both%20positive%20and%20negative%2C%20is%20felt%20more%20intensely%20under%20bright%20lights.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20feel%20more%20at%20ease%20and%20less%20activated%2C%20keeping%20the%20lights%20lower%20actually%20helps%20you%20calm%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-light-bulb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20out%20a%20soft%20white%20lightbulb%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20bright%20white%20bulb%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-desk-lamp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadding%20a%20lamp%20on%20a%20side%20table%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20change%20the%20entire%20mood%20of%20a%20room.%20Adding%20a%20dimmer%20switch%20softens%20the%20overhead%20lighting%20for%20a%20smoother%2C%20more%20gentle%20transition%20from%20day-to-night.%20Experiment%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20lighting%20options%20for%20every%20room%20since%20it's%20not%20always%20a%20one-bulb-fits-all%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20hack%3A%20Swap%20out%20your%20lampshade%20for%20something%20darker%20or%20moodier%20to%20provide%20a%20more%20relaxed%20ambiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20to%20shift%20your%20lighting%20strategy%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESoften%20your%20color%20palette%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22urban%20outfitters%20bedroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5febb530b7ab82001943e849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUrban%20Outfitters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EColors%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4383146%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevoke%20feelings%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20why%20we're%20drawn%20to%20some%20and%20repelled%20by%20others.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20first%20lessons%20artists%20learn%20in%20design%20school%20since%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-the-color-red-influences-our-behavior%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered%20wall%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20exactly%20have%20you%20feeling%20at%20ease%2C%20while%20a%20light%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Fyour-personal-renaissance%2F201810%2Fsurprising-research-the-color-blue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblue%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20grey%20might%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Frankel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20big%20impact%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-paint-according-to-experts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaint%20one%20or%20all%20of%20the%20walls%20in%20a%20room%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20also%20cultivate%20a%20color%20palette%20with%20less%20effort%20and%20money%20by%20bringing%20in%20blankets%2C%20lamps%2C%20curtains%2C%20and%20accent%20decorations%20all%20in%20a%20certain%20shade.%20Start%20by%20walking%20around%20your%20house%20and%20pulling%20together%20all%20the%20odds%20and%20ends%20you%20have%20in%20one%20color%20palette%2C%20then%20grouping%20them%20in%20a%20room%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20at%20new%20paint%20or%20accessory%20colors%2C%20interior%20designer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emmaberyl.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmma%20Kemper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20recommended%20warm%20neutrals%20to%20foster%20a%20sense%20of%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20to%20making%20your%20neutrals%20feel%20energizing%20instead%20of%20stale%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20to%20layer%20in%20different%20textures%20and%20different%20shades%20in%20the%20same%20overall%20color-family%20so%20that%20your%20eyes%20still%20bounce%20around%20a%20room%20and%20things%20feel%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20don't%20forget%20about%20the%20ceiling%2C%20said%20Nunnerley.%20It%20doesn't%20always%20have%20to%20be%20white%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20pared-down%20version%20of%20the%20wall%20color%20to%20create%20a%20seamless%20flow%20that's%20soothing%20and%20uninterrupted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20to%20improve%20your%20color%20palette%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EClean%20up%20clutter%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22small%20closet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5febb8bca644880018193c12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EElena%20Elisseeva%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20of%20us%2C%20a%20messy%20desk%2C%20sink%20full%20of%20dishes%2C%20or%20bedroom%20floor%20littered%20with%20clothes%20slowly%20eats%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20mind.%20Meanwhile%2C%20other%20people%20just%20don't%20seem%20to%20notice%20the%20mess%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20certainly%20feel%20it%3A%20Meghan%20Marcum%2C%20PsyD.%2C%20chief%20psychologist%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famfmtreatment.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20Mission%20For%20Michael%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mental%20Health%20Center%20in%20San%20Juan%20Capistrano%2C%20California%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20people%20with%20cluttered%20homes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F20053034%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20stress%20hormone%20cortisol%20in%20their%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToo%20much%20cortisol%20has%20a%20large%20impact%20on%20our%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%2C%20including%20things%20as%20simple%20as%20feeling%20more%20anxious%20and%20activated.%20%26quot%3BAn%20organized%20home%20helps%20you%20feel%20at%20ease%20and%20prepares%20your%20body%20for%20rest%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20begin%2C%20everything%20in%20your%20space%20should%20have%20a%20deliberate%20purpose%20and%2C%20as%20Marie%20Kondo%20reminds%2C%20fill%20you%20with%20joy%2C%20not%20anxiety.%20%26quot%3BTake%20advantage%20of%20closet%20and%20cabinet%20space%20for%20items%20that%20are%20less%20visually%20appealing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kemper%20recommended.%20%26quot%3BFor%20items%20you%20need%20to%20store%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20use%20pleasing%20storage%20pieces%20like%20woven%2C%20lidded%20baskets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20simple%20storage%20bins%20at%20the%20dollar%20store%20and%20cheap%2C%20funky%20ones%20at%20thrift%20stores.%20Repurpose%20old%20containers%2C%20especially%20from%20bigger%20bulk%20items%2C%20to%20keep%20items%20in%20closets%20and%20cabinets%20organized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKemper%20says%20to%20follow%20the%20rule%20of%20three%C2%A0for%20the%20knick-knacks%20or%20sentimental%20items%20you%20want%20to%20display.%20This%20means%20grouping%20together%20items%20in%20threes%20and%20playing%20with%20differing%20heights%20and%20colors%20to%20add%20extra%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftidying-up-with-marie-kondo-organizing-tips-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E16%20of%20the%20best%20organizing%20tips%20from%20Marie%20Kondo's%20new%20Netflix%20series%20'Tidying%20Up'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-organization-easy-ideas-for-social-distancing-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reorganize%20and%20declutter%20without%20buying%20anything%20new%20while%20social%20distancing%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-organize-bedroom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E8%20practical%20tips%20organize%20your%20bedroom%2C%20according%20to%20professional%20organizers%20and%20interior%20designers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EClean%20up%20with%20these%20picks%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInvest%20in%20soft%20and%20comfortable%20textiles%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%220H8A3094_1200x%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fe390bcedf89200180938d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYaYa%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20are%20in%20a%20negative%20mindset%2C%20they're%20hyperaware%20of%20tactile%20stimuli%20(i.e.%2C%20the%20way%20things%20feel%20to%20the%20touch)%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20reach%20for%20soft%20or%20pleasant%20textures%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.warrington.ufl.edu%2Fdepartments%2Fmkt%2Fdocs%2Fjaniszewski%2FAffect-Gating.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Journal%20of%20Consumer%20Research%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoft%20items%20like%20a%20cozy%20bathrobe%2C%20a%20fluffy%20comforter%2C%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-weighted-blanket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweighted%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20help%20you%20feel%20more%20calm%20and%20relaxed.%20For%20Chicago-based%20interior%20designer%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.karamann.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKara%20Mann%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20best%20luxe%20indulgence%20is%20bedding%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sheets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-quality%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-comforter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomforters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-throw-pillows%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrow%20pillows%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20what%20makes%20the%20most%20sense%20for%20the%20room%20you're%20focused%20on%20creating%20calm%20in%2C%20and%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20decide%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20cashmere%20or%20alpaca%20wrap%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-sweaters-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweater%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20silk%20nightgown%20that%20can%20move%20from%20room-to-room%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETry%20these%20to%20add%20comfortable%20textiles%20throughout%20your%20home%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-create-a-calm-home%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fe26da9edf892001809362e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-create-a-calm-home%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Design%20elements%20like%20natural%20light%2C%20lower%20lighting%2C%20and%20better%20organization%20can%20help%20create%20visual%20tranquility%20and%20improve%20anxiety%20and%20mood%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Tigar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-create-a-calm-home%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20bought%20an%20infrared%20sauna%20blanket%20on%20Amazon%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20been%20more%20energized%20and%20less%20bloated%20in%20my%20life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2261Oe2RjvQrL._SL1024_%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c66da001631a378802cd0eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20recently%20purchased%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrared%20sauna%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20best%20wellness%20decision%20I've%20ever%20made.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudies%20suggest%20that%20infrared-light%20therapy%20has%20a%20bevy%20of%20medical%20benefits%2C%20including%20reducing%20inflammation%2C%20clearing%20skin%20issues%2C%20improving%20digestion%2C%20contributing%20to%20weight%20loss%2C%20and%20easing%20anxiety.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors%20agree%20that%2020%20minutes%20of%20infrared%20sweating%20two%20to%20three%20times%20a%20week%20strengthens%20the%20cardiovascular%20system.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20personally%20use%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrared%20sauna%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2050%20minutes%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I've%20never%20felt%20more%20energized%20and%20glowing%20(or%20less%20bloated)%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20first%20to%20admit%20I've%20tried%20some%20wacky%20things%20in%20the%20name%20of%20wellness.%20I%20once%20ate%20raw%20garlic%20cloves%20every%20morning%20for%20two%20weeks%20straight%20as%20a%20natural%20alternative%20to%20antibiotics.%20(Not%20advised%2C%20if%20only%20for%20the%20garlic%20breath.)%20I%20brush%20my%20hair%20with%20a%20comb%20carved%20from%20a%20clear%20quartz%20crystal%20to%20purify%20my%20crown%20chakra.%20(Totally%20advised%2C%20if%20only%20for%20the%20aesthetic.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20dropped%20%24450%20on%20an%20infrared%20sauna%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0so%20I%20could%20%26quot%3Bdetox%26quot%3B%20daily%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20my%20own%20home%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20one's%20not%20as%20%26quot%3Bout%20there%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20sounds.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fhealthy-lifestyle%2Fconsumer-health%2Fexpert-answers%2Finfrared-sauna%2Ffaq-20057954%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperts%20agree%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20infrared%20sauna%20therapy%20can%20improve%20digestion%2C%20reduce%20pain%20and%20inflammation%2C%20benefit%20cardiovascular%20health%2C%20and%20even%20clear%20up%20acne.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20infrared%20sauna%20therapy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20experienced%20the%20benefits%20of%20infrared%20sauna%20therapy%20firsthand%20almost%20a%20year%20ago.%20It%20was%20two%20months%20before%20my%20wedding%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20fit%20into%20my%20dress.%20Desperate%20to%20lose%20a%20little%20weight%20before%20the%20big%20day%2C%20I%20added%20biweekly%20sauna%20appointments%20to%20my%20nutrition%20and%20fitness%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20I%20noticed%20most%20after%20a%20couple%20months%20of%20regular%20sweat%20sessions%20wasn't%20the%20weight%20loss%20(although%20it%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehelped%20in%20that%20department%20%E2%80%94%20my%20wedding%20dress%20fit%20like%20a%20glove).%20It%20was%20how%20energized%20I%20was%20afterward.%20How%20completely%20glow-y%20my%20skin%20looked.%20How%20cooking%20for%20an%20hour%20at%20170%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20motivated%20me%20to%20make%20better%20choices%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%3B%20I%20just%20%3Cem%3Efelt%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehealthier%20and%20happier%2C%20and%20wanted%20that%20feeling%20to%20last%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dr.%20Josh%20Axe%2C%20D.N.M.%2C%20C.N.S.%2C%20D.C.%20%E2%80%94%20the%20founder%20of%20Ancient%20Nutrition%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdraxe.com%2Fabout-dr-josh-axe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrAxe.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20author%20of%20the%20upcoming%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdraxe.com%2Fdr-axe-keto-diet-book%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKeto%20Diet%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20this%20all%20checks%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfrared%20saunas%20(sometimes%20called%20far-infrared%20saunas%20or%20near-infrared%20saunas)%20are%20a%20type%20of%20sauna%20that%20uses%20heat%20and%20light%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20infrared%20light%20waves%2C%20to%20help%20'detoxify'%20the%20body%20via%20sweat%20and%20to%20promote%20relaxation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BProponents%20of%20infrared%20saunas%20often%20turn%20to%20this%20type%20of%20holistic%20treatment%20in%20hopes%20that%20sessions%20can%20provide%20joint%20and%20muscle%20support%2C%20speed%20up%20the%20metabolism%2C%20promote%20weight%20loss%2C%20help%20rejuvenate%20the%20skin%2C%20improve%20circulation%2C%20promote%20cardiovascular%20healing%2C%20and%20help%20with%20sleep%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr.%20Axe%20said%20scientific%20study%20in%20this%20area%20is%20limited%20but%20promising.%20But%20if%20you're%20a%20believer%20in%20anecdotal%20evidence%2C%20take%20my%20word%20for%20it%3A%20Infrared%20sauna%20sweating%20is%20better%20than%20a%20juice%20cleanse.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20indulged%20in%20regular%20infrared%20treatments%20at%20Shape%20House%2C%20an%20%26quot%3Burban%20sweat%20lodge%26quot%3B%20with%20locations%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%20City.%20While%20typical%20sweat%20lodges%20feature%20steam%20saunas%2C%20Shape%20House%20uses%20far-infrared%20technology.%20You're%20essentially%20wrapped%20up%20like%20a%20burrito%20in%20a%20plastic%20covering%2C%20which%20is%20then%20heated%20up%20to%20170%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20for%2050%20minutes%20using%20infrared%20light%20to%20build%20heat%20in%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfrared%20saunas%20differ%20from%20regular%20heated%20saunas%20because%20they%20emit%20light%20that%20directly%20penetrates%20your%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20Axe%20said.%20There's%20no%20steam%2C%20no%20humidity%2C%20and%20no%20hot%20air%3B%20this%20makes%20it%20%3Cem%3Emuch%3C%2Fem%3E%20easier%20to%20breathe%20and%20withstand%20high%20temperatures%20for%20a%20longer%20amount%20of%20time.%20But%20at%20about%20%2450%20per%20appointment%2C%20my%20Shape%20House%20habit%20wasn't%20one%20that%20I%20could%20keep%20up%20without%20that%20wedding%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20went%20without%20regular%20sweat%20sessions%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20which%20only%20confirmed%20how%20powerfully%20they%20affected%20me%3A%20My%20digestion%20felt%20sluggish%2C%20my%20stomach%20was%20bloated%2C%20my%20acne%20returned%2C%20and%20I%20was%20low%20energy%20and%20anxious%20more%20often%20than%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20I%20looked%20into%20at-home%20infrared%20sauna%20blankets%20to%20get%20back%20on%20track%20on%20a%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20search%20for%20an%20affordable%2C%20at-home%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Einfrared%20sauna%20therapy%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Ebrought%20me%20to%20Amazon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfrared%20sauna%20blankets%20are%20similar%20to%20heavy%20sleeping%20bags%3B%20you%20enclose%20yourself%20in%20one%20as%20it%20emits%20infrared%20rays%20and%20builds%20body%20heat%2C%26quot%3B%20Axe%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20advantages%20to%20using%20an%20infrared%20blanket%20include%20affordability%3B%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20compact%2C%20lightweight%2C%20and%20portable%3B%20the%20convenience%20of%20being%20able%20to%20use%20it%20at%20home%3B%20and%20versatility%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20be%20used%20in%20bed%2C%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20or%20in%20a%20chair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20can%20run%20anywhere%20from%20%24100%20to%20%241%2C000%2C%20and%20after%20doing%20extensive%20research%2C%20I%20found%20%26quot%3BThe%20One%26quot%3B%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGizmo%20Supply%203%20Zone%20Digital%20Far-Infrared%20Heat%20Sauna%20Blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20priced%20at%20%24450%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20cost%20of%20one%20month's%20worth%20of%20Shape%20House%20treatments%20%E2%80%94%20with%20more%20than%2070%20five-star%20reviews.%20Just%20two%20days%20later%2C%20it%20was%20at%20my%20door.%20(Thank%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-prime-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Prime%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetting%20up%20and%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGizmo%20Supply%20infrared%20sauna%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGizmo%20Supply%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20super%20easy%20to%20put%20together.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20control%20box%20and%20a%20sleeping-bag-esque%20blanket%2C%20which%20need%20to%20be%20connected%20via%20a%20series%20of%20three%20clearly%20labeled%20wires.%20Each%20wire%20feeds%20into%20a%20section%20of%20the%20blanket%2C%20and%20all%20three%20sections%20can%20be%20separately%20heated%20anywhere%20between%2035%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%2085%20degrees%20Celsius%20(about%2095%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20to%20185%20degrees%20Fahrenheit)%20for%20up%20to%20an%20hour.%20You%20just%20select%20your%20desired%20temp%20and%20time%2C%20get%20in%2C%20sweat%20profusely%20and%20semi-uncomfortably%2C%20and%20wait%20for%20it%20to%20beep%20when%20the%20session%20is%20over%20%E2%80%A6%20kind%20of%20like%20an%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221025%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gizmo%20Supply%203%20Zone%20Digital%20Far%20Infrared%20Blanket%20Specs%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6484b474c5872c9e3575c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGizmo%20Supply%20Co%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrequent%2C%20short%20infrared%20sauna%20sessions%20seem%20to%20be%20effective%20for%20providing%20the%20health%20benefits%20mentioned%20above%2C%26quot%3B%20Axe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20linked%20%26quot%3B20%20minute%20treatments%20three%20times%20weekly%20over%20a%20period%20of%20two%20to%20three%20months%26quot%3B%20with%20increased%20heart%20strength%2C%20so%20that's%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start.%20I%20personally%20follow%20the%20Shape%20House%20method%20and%20sweat%20for%2050%20minutes%20at%2080%20degrees%20Celsius%20every%20single%20day.%20I'm%20certifiably%20obsessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20I%20started%20my%20daily%20at-home%20treatments%2C%20I%20noticed%20an%20almost%20immediate%20improvement%20in%20my%20bloating%2C%20skin%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20mood.%20It%20turns%20out%2C%20a%20good%20sweat%20will%20do%20that%20to%20you.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweating%20is%20the%20body's%20natural%20method%20of%20detox%2C%20and%20far-infrared%20heat%20is%20said%20to%20induce%20a%20whopping%20seven%20times%20more%20sweat%20than%20a%20standard%20steam%20sauna.%20This%20essentially%20flushes%20toxins%20out%20of%20the%20body%20via%20a%20process%20called%20%26quot%3Blymphatic%20drainage%2C%26quot%3B%20boosts%20metabolism%2C%20and%20increases%20your%20energy%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%20internal%20flush%2C%20the%20act%20of%20sweating%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bskin%20detox%26quot%3B%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%20As%20your%20pores%20open%20and%20sweat%20pours%20through%2C%20its%20antibacterial%20properties%20kill%20acne-causing%20bacteria%20and%20rinse%20away%20any%20dirt%20and%20debris%20sitting%20on%20the%20skin's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAside%20from%20your%20liver%2C%20your%20skin%20is%20one%20of%20your%20greatest%20tools%20to%20detoxify%20your%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Katie%20Dunlop%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flovesweatfitness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELove%20Sweat%20Fitness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20that%20it's%20our%20largest%20organ%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20our%20first%20line%20of%20defense%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sweat%20allows%20us%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20toxins%20through%20the%20skin%2C%20leaving%20it%20fresh%20and%20rejuvenated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSweating%20also%20means%20increased%20blood%20circulation%20throughout%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20your%20heart%20rate%20increases%2C%20so%20does%20the%20blood%20flow%20to%20the%20skin%2C%20bringing%20along%20with%20it%20lots%20of%20vital%20nutrients%20and%20fresh%20oxygen.%20The%20benefit%20is%20it's%20happening%20from%20the%20inside%20out%2C%20so%20not%20only%20is%20your%20skin%20getting%20the%20amazing%20oxygen%20and%20nutrients%20it%20needs%20to%20promote%20collagen%20growth%2C%20but%20you're%20also%20able%20to%20detox%20and%20expel%20toxins%20simultaneously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20swear%2C%20my%20skin%20never%20looks%20more%20rosy%20and%20glow-y%20than%20after%20a%20sauna%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrared%20power%20is%20more%20than%20just%20physical%2C%20though.%20With%20regular%20use%2C%20I%20find%20my%20anxiety%20symptoms%20are%20lessened.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20partly%20because%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20lying%20in%20the%20blanket%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20gives%20me%20a%20chance%20to%20meditate%20and%20reflect%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20times%20of%20my%20day%20not%20consumed%20by%20my%20laptop%20or%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20believed%20that%20infrared%20saunas%20promote%20mental%20health%20through%20activating%20the%20parasympathetic%20nervous%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Axe%20said.%20%26quot%3BActivation%20of%20the%20parasympathetic%20nervous%20system%20helps%20to%20make%20you%20feel%20calm%2C%20allows%20the%20body%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20and%20counteracts%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20sympathetic%20nervous%20system's%20'fight%20or%20flight%20response.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20potential%20downsides%20and%20health%20concerns%20to%20consider%20before%20using%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20amazing%20as%20I%20feel%20inside%20and%20out%20after%20sweating%2C%20I%20have%20to%20be%20honest%3A%20The%20sauna%20itself%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20pleasant%20experience.%20It%20gets%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20to%20state%20the%20obvious%20%E2%80%94%20and%20really%2C%20really%20sweaty%2C%20and%20it%20definitely%20takes%20some%20willpower%20to%20make%20it%20through%2030%20to%2050%20minutes%20in%20the%20blanket.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20common%20reported%20side%20effects%20are%20mild%20to%20moderate%20heat%20discomfort%20and%20intolerance%2C%20low%20blood%20pressure%2C%20lightheadedness%2C%20and%20claustrophobia%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Axe.%20He%20said%20it's%20safe%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20though%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20those%20who%20can't%20normally%20tolerate%20other%20treatments%20that%20involve%20heat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20who%20has%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20a%20history%20of%20heart%20problems%2C%20or%20who%20takes%20daily%20medications%20should%20get%20their%20doctor's%20approval%20before%20beginning%20infrared%20sauna%20treatments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20It's%20also%20recommended%20to%20wear%20head-to-toe%20cotton%20while%20you're%20in%20the%20blanket%20to%20safely%20soak%20up%20excess%20sweat%2C%20and%20to%20hydrate%20like%20crazy%20before%20and%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20realize%20that%20spending%20nearly%20an%20hour%20of%20my%20day%2C%20every%20day%2C%20wrapped%20up%20like%20a%20sweaty%20burrito%20sounds%20strange%20%E2%80%94%20Gwyneth%20Paltrow%20Goop-level%20strange.%20But%20honestly%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gizmosupplyco.com%2Fcollections%2Fsauna-gizmo%2Fproducts%2Fgizmo-supply-3-zone-digital-far-infrared-fir-heat-sauna-blanket-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrared%20sauna%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20most%20practical%20wellness%20purchase%20I've%20ever%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20become%20my%20life's%20cure-all.%20Feeling%20bloated%20and%20gross%3F%20Time%20for%20a%20sweat%20sesh.%20Skin%20dull%20and%20dry%3F%20Sweat%20sesh.%20Hungover%3F%20Puffy%20eyes%3F%20Stressed%3F%20I%20just%20sweat%2C%20sweat%2C%20sweat%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhoever%20said%20not%20to%20sweat%20the%20small%20stuff%20%3Cem%3Eclearly%3C%2Fem%3E%20just%20needed%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20an%20infrared%20sauna%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgizmo-supply-infrared-sauna-therapy-blanket-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6c5fab26289863ea240e53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgizmo-supply-infrared-sauna-therapy-blanket-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gizmo%20digital%20infrared%20sauna%20therapy%20blanket%20is%20the%20best%20wellness%20purchase%20I've%20made.%20I've%20never%20been%20more%20energized%20and%20less%20bloated%20in%20my%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehoffman%40businessinsider.com%20(Jessica%20DeFino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgizmo-supply-infrared-sauna-therapy-blanket-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20polls%3A%20From%20Perambur%20to%20Kolathur