t%20parts%20of%20the%20South.%20Finally%2C%20on%20June%2019%2C%201865%2C%20Union%20army%20soldiers%20reached%20Gavelston%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20announced%20the%20end%20of%20slavery%2C%20thus%20beginning%20the%20celebration%20of%20Juneteenth.%20%26quot%3BThe%20significance%20of%20Juneteenth%20is%20that%20freedom%20came%20but%20it%20took%20the%20Emancipation%20Proclamation%2C%20it%20took%20a%20Civil%20War%2C%20and%20it%20also%20took%20the%2013th%20Amendment%20to%20free%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mary%20Elliott%2C%20a%20curator%20of%20American%20slavery%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnmaahc.si.edu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmithsonian%20National%20Museum%20of%20African%20American%20History%20and%20Culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20recorded%20celebrations%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnmaahc.si.edu%2Fblog-post%2Fhistorical-legacy-juneteenth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuneteenth%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20place%20around%201867%2C%20and%20the%20holiday%20was%20originally%20celebrated%20among%20communities%20in%20Galveston%2C%20Austin%2C%20and%20Houston%20in%20Texas%2C%20and%20in%20other%20southern%20states%20through%20parades%2C%20prayer%2C%20and%20other%20festivities.%20However%2C%20as%20time%20has%20passed%20the%20holiday%20has%20become%20more%20popular%20and%20widely%20celebrated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20many%20companies%20making%20Juneteenth%20an%20official%20company%20holiday%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffas.org%2Fsgp%2Fcrs%2Fmisc%2FR44865.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2045%20states%20officially%20recognizing%20the%20holiday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20become%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20that%20we%20learn%20how%20to%20celebrate%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20truly%20honors%20its%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that's%20important%20is%20thinking%20about%20Juneteenth%20as%20a%20celebration%20but%20also%20a%20commemoration%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elliott%2C%20who%20emphasized%20looking%20at%20Juneteenth%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20other%20US%20celebrations%20of%20freedom%20such%20as%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July.%20Juneteenth%20is%20an%20important%20time%20for%20all%20Americans%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20freedom.%20%26quot%3BIf%20everyone's%20going%20to%20celebrate%20this%20holiday%20or%20commemorate%20this%20occasion%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20very%20important%20moment%20to%20pause%20and%20reflect%20on%20freedom%20and%20enslavement%20in%20this%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elliott.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe've%20compiled%20five%20ways%20to%20celebrate%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecommemorate%20Juneteenth%20this%20year%2C%20through%20supporting%20Black-owned%20businesses%20and%20restaurants%2C%20reading%20books%20by%20Black%20authors%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20supporting%20various%20causes%20and%20organizations.%20Elliott%20also%20recommends%20taking%20the%20holiday%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20history%20of%20slavery%20and%20the%20treatment%20of%20African%20Americans%20in%20this%20country%20by%20reading%20relevant%20historical%20documents%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.battlefields.org%2Flearn%2Fprimary-sources%2Fgeneral-order-no-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnion%20General%20Gordon%20Granger's%20General%20Order%20No.%203%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archives.gov%2Fexhibits%2Ffeatured-documents%2Femancipation-proclamation%2Ftranscript.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Emancipation%20Proclamation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconstitutioncenter.org%2Finteractive-constitution%2Famendment%2Famendment-xiii%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13th%20Amendment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20use%20Juneteenth%20to%20empower%20themselves%2C%20to%20raise%20up%20issues%2C%20and%20to%20reflect%20on%20where%20they%20came%20from%2C%20where%20they%20are%2C%20and%20where%20they%20have%20yet%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elliott.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20celebrate%20this%20year%2C%20these%20five%20options%20are%20a%20great%20place%20to%20start.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20five%20ways%20to%20celebrate%20Juneteenth%20this%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBuy%20from%20Black-owned%20businesses%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black-owned%20menswear%20brands%20collage%20image%20featuring%20clothing%20like%20a%20brown%20hat%20from%20Telfar%2C%20a%20green%20jacket%20from%20Tier%2C%20and%20more%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c3afc06d855e0018157a3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDenim%20Tears%2C%20Telfar%2C%20TIER%2C%20UNION%20LOS%20ANGELES%2C%20Martine%20Rose%2C%20Connor%20McKnight%2C%20Fear%20of%20God%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FINSIDER%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20many%20Black-owned%20brands%20are%20hosting%20sales%20in%20celebration%20of%20Juneteenth%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20time%20to%20shop%20with%20them%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20We've%20curated%20a%20list%20of%20brands%20that%20offer%20natural%20candles%2C%20stunning%20art%20prints%2C%20unique%20accessories%2C%20and%20even%20targeted%20skincare%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20brands%20featured%20below%20are%20available%20at%20major%20retailers%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-1009-20%26h%3Db6cc18ea0e862123e809722d424c98de65a5a9669e6ad69d8abc2e18dbf063a0%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f433a8%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsupport-black-owned-businesses%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fw