20keep%20a%20sophisticated%20and%20cohesive%20look%20throughout%20your%20tablescape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMikasa%20offers%20many%20sets%20in%20stainless%20steel%20with%20gold%20accents%2C%20so%20you%20can%20also%20mix%20and%20match%20this%20set%20with%20others%20for%20added%20visual%20appeal%20that%20still%20has%20a%20cohesive%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20flatware%20set%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20some%20guidance%20from%20experts%20about%20what%20to%20look%20for%20when%20you're%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20flatware%2C%20along%20with%20what%20we%20considered%20when%20choosing%20our%20top%20picks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EPrice%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20expect%20to%20pay%20upwards%20of%20%24300%20to%20fully%20outfit%20your%20home%20with%20a%20high-quality%20set%2C%20but%20you%20can%20go%20as%20low%20as%20%2430%20if%20you're%20selective%20about%20the%20number%20and%20type%20of%20utensils%20you%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ENumber%20of%20pieces%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20your%20budget%2C%20Whitmore%20recommends%20looking%20for%20products%20that%20contain%20the%20core%20five%20utensils.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20shopping%20for%20flatware%2C%20you%20want%20to%20be%20sure%20each%20set%20comes%20with%20a%20dinner%20knife%2C%20dinner%20fork%2C%20salad%20fork%2C%20dinner%20spoon%2C%20and%20teaspoon%3B%20this%20will%20cover%20everything%20you'll%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Whitmore.%20%26quot%3BI%20prefer%20to%20plan%20for%20large%20gatherings%2C%20so%20I%20like%20to%20buy%20sets%20of%20at%20least%20eight%20but%20often%2010%20or%2012.%20It's%20never%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20have%20extra%20because%20items%20like%20spoons%20are%20used%20more%20often%20(for%20cereal%2C%20coffee%2C%20etc).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EOpen%20stock%20vs.%20sets%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou'll%20need%20to%20decide%20if%20you%20want%20to%20buy%20individual%20pieces%20(also%20known%20as%20open%20stock)%2C%20pieces%20by%20the%20place%20setting%2C%20or%20a%20box%20set%20that%20typically%20comes%20with%20service%20for%20four%2C%20six%2C%20eight%2C%20or%2012%20people.%20Here%20is%20some%20more%20information%20about%20each%20type%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpen%20stock%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Buying%20individual%20pieces%2C%20also%20known%20as%20open%20stock%2C%20is%20great%20if%20you're%20missing%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20utensils%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20college%20student%2C%20or%20if%20you%20live%20alone%20and%20only%20need%20a%20few%20pieces.%20It's%20also%20a%20great%20option%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20temporary%20or%20easily%20replaceable%20flatware%2C%20like%20if%20you%20need%20to%20stock%20a%20rental%20property%20you%20own%20or%20if%20you%20have%20extra%20mouths%20to%20feed%20for%20a%20special%20occasion.%20However%2C%20many%20open%20stock%20items%20aren't%20the%20most%20durable%2C%20so%20they%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20with%20daily%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20the%20place%20setting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20If%20you%20buy%20flatware%20by%20the%20place%20setting%2C%20each%20box%20usually%20comes%20with%20five%20pieces%3A%20a%20dinner%20fork%2C%20salad%20fork%2C%20a%20dessert%20spoon%2C%20a%20soup%20spoon%2C%20and%20a%20dinner%20knife.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20option%20if%20you%20want%20to%20choose%20the%20number%20of%20place%20settings%20to%20suit%20your%20household%20(since%20box%20sets%20usually%20come%20in%20set%20quantities)%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20replace%20missing%20or%20damaged%20flatware%2C%20or%20would%20like%20a%20few%20extra%20place%20settings%20for%20backup%20when%20hosting%20guests.%20A%20quality%20product%20typically%20runs%20between%20%2430%20to%20%2450%20per%20setting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBox%20sets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20You'll%20get%20more%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%20if%20you%20invest%20in%20a%20box%20set.%20A%20box%20set%20comes%20in%20services%20from%20four%20to%20up%20to%2012%20people%20(some%20retailers%20even%20have%20service%20for%20up%20to%2016%20people)%2C%20and%20features%20the%20same%20five%20pieces%20found%20in%20individual%20place%20settings.%20A%20box%20set%20with%20service%20for%20four%20typically%20has%2020%20total%20pieces%2C%20a%20set%20for%20service%20for%20eight%20typically%20has%2040%20pieces%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20sets%20for%20service%20for%2012%20or%20more%20also%20usually%20come%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostess%20set%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20extra%20serveware%20like%20solid%20and%20slotted%20serving%20spoons%2C%20a%20meat%20fork%2C%20and%20soup%20ladle%20that%20match%20the%20design%20of%20the%20flatware.%20A%20box%20set%20is%20especially%20useful%20if%20you%20have%20a%20family%20of%20at%20least%20four%20people%20or%20often%20host%20dinner%20for%20a%20large%20number%20of%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EBrand%20reputation%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20whether%20you%20opt%20for%20open%20stock%20or%20box%20sets%2C%20experts%20said%20you'll%20get%20the%20best%20results%20by%20selecting%20products%20from%20a%20known%20brand.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20shopping%20for%20flatware%2C%20always%20buy%20from%20a%20reputable%20flatware%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jefferson%20Mack%2C%20flatware%20and%20metal%20product%20designer%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mackmetal.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emackmetal.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20can%20buy%20replacements%2010%20years%20down%20the%20road.%26quot%3B%20These%20companies%20are%20also%20usually%20forthcoming%20about%20materials%20and%20manufacturing%20methods%2C%20offer%20longer%20warranties%2C%20and%20have%20robust%20customer%20service.%20All%20the%20picks%20in%20our%20guide%20are%20vetted%20by%20experts%2C%20come%20with%20at%20least%20a%2025-year%20warranty%2C%20or%20are%20produced%20by%20a%20well-known%20flatware%20brand%20that%20has%20been%20in%20business%20for%20at%20least%2050%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EReturn%20policy%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20possible%2C%20see%20a%20complete%20place%20setting%20in%20person%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20size%20feels%20right%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marian%20Parsons%2C%20artist%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.missmustardseed.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustard%20Seed%20Interiors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20do%20decide%20to%20shop%20online%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20buy%20from%20a%20reputable%20retailer%20that%20has%20a%20robust%20return%20policy%2C%20since%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20evaluate%20the%20comfort%20and%20weight%20of%20your%20flatware%20until%20you%20try%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETypes%20of%20flatware%20metals%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Different%20types%20of%20flatware%20shown%20in%20silver%20and%20gold%20colors%20on%20a%20white%20table%20cloth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd9322b1803a80018adfa5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Marquand%2FEyeEm%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlatware%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20materials%20including%20stainless%20steel%2C%20sterling%20silver%2C%20and%20metals%20combined%20with%20other%20materials%20like%20resin%2C%20wood%2C%20and%20plastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EStainless%20steel%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20everyday%20use%2C%20look%20for%20stainless%20steel%20flatware.%20Stainless%20steel%20flatware%20is%20primarily%20made%20from%20chromium%20and%20nickel%2C%20which%20are%20both%20durable%20and%20resistant%20to%20corrosion.%20When%20shopping%20for%20stainless%20steel%20flatware%2C%20you'll%20notice%20a%20number%20like%2018%2F10%2C%2018%2F8%2C%20or%2018%2F0%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20percentage%20of%20chromium%20(the%20first%20number)%20and%20nickel%20(the%20second%20number)%20in%20the%20metal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20experts%20recommend%20opting%20for%2018%2F10%20stainless%20steel%20since%20the%20nickel%20content%20boosts%20durability%20and%20adds%20a%20soft%2C%20silver-like%20luster%20to%20flatware.%20It's%20also%20what%20makes%20flatware%20more%20expensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20number%20isn't%20everything%2C%20however%2C%20said%20Mack%3B%20most%20reputable%20manufacturers%20sell%20flatware%20that%20is%20durable%20and%20rust-resistant%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20type%20of%20stainless%20steel%20used.%20If%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20something%20durable%20at%20a%20great%20value%2C%2018%2F0%20is%20still%20a%20good%20option%3B%20you%20just%20won't%20get%20the%20high-polish%20finish%20and%20superior%20rust-resistance%20nickel%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EStamped%20vs.%20forged%20stainless%20steel%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20notice%20the%20product%20description%20mention%20whether%20the%20flatware%20is%20stamped%20or%20forged.%20Stamped%20stainless%20is%20cut%20out%20like%20a%20cookie%20cutter%20from%20a%20big%20piece%20of%20stainless%20steel%2C%20while%20forged%20flatware%20is%20made%20from%20a%20heated%20block%20of%20steel%20that's%20pounded%20into%20shape.%20Because%20of%20the%20heating%20process%2C%20forged%20flatware%20is%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20stamped.%20If%20the%20product%20description%20doesn't%20include%20if%20it's%20stamped%20or%20forged%2C%20compare%20the%20knife%20blade%20to%20the%20handle.%20If%20they're%20similar%20in%20thickness%20and%20if%20it's%20lightweight%2C%20it's%20most%20likely%20stamped%2C%20which%20won't%20hold%20up%20as%20well%20as%20forged%20for%20everyday%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ESterling%20silver%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESterling%20silver%20is%20also%20durable%2C%20but%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20stainless%20steel%20and%20requires%20polishing%20since%20it%20can%20tarnish%2C%20developing%20a%20dark-colored%20coat%20when%20exposed%20to%20gases%20in%20the%20air%20over%20time.%20We%20think%20stainless%20steel%20is%20the%20best%20bet%20for%20most%20people%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20a%20collector%20or%20prefer%20a%20vintage%20aesthetic%2C%20you%20may%20opt%20for%20sterling%20silver.%20With%20the%20right%20care%2C%20a%20sterling%20silver%20set%20can%20last%20you%20for%20years%2C%20increase%20in%20value%2C%20and%20become%20a%20family%20heirloom%20you%20can%20pass%20down%20from%20generation%20to%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20far%20too%20many%20beautiful%20sets%20of%20silver%20flatware%20sitting%20in%20a%20box%20or%20drawer%20unused%2C%26quot%3B%20Parsons%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20silver%20is%20stored%20properly%20or%20used%20daily%2C%20it%20requires%20very%20little%20polishing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-flatware%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776869002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fda25921803a80018adfc01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-flatware%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20of%20us%20use%20flatware%20or%20silverware%20every%20day%3B%20here%20are%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20flatware%20to%20suit%20every%20budget%2C%20need%2C%20and%20style.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Farima%20Ferguson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-flatware%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20dealing%20with%20dozens%20of%20layovers%20as%20a%20frequent%20flyer%2C%20I've%20found%205%20ways%20to%20make%20them%20actually%20enjoyable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Istanbul%20airport%20with%20plants%2C%20shops%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11f01bfebcc4d029d9498%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20a%20frequent%20traveler%2C%20I've%20learned%20some%20solid%20tips%20for%20dealing%20with%20layovers%20and%20making%20them%20as%20fun%20as%20possible.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20used%20to%20dread%20layovers%20in%20airports%2C%20but%20I've%20now%20found%20ways%20to%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-priority-pass-membership-credit-card-capital-one-review-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirport-lounge%20access%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20lifesaver%20on%20long%20travel%20days%2C%20and%20staying%20busy%20at%20the%20airport%20is%20key.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20sometimes%20leave%20the%20airport%20to%20explore%20nearby%20if%20my%20layover%20is%20longer%20than%20seven%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20travelers%20dread%20layovers%20when%20flying%2C%20but%20I've%20actually%20come%20to%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20frequent%20flyer%2C%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20airports.%20In%20just%20one%20year%2C%20I%20flew%20around%20the%20world%20to%20Japan%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Ghana%2C%20and%20Svalbard%2C%20among%20other%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20my%20home%20airport%20is%20small%20and%20has%20few%20direct%20flights.%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20my%20flight%20itineraries%20almost%20always%20require%20at%20least%20one%20layover%2C%20sometimes%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20I%20felt%20miserable%20on%20travel%20days.%20I%20hated%20spending%20layovers%20in%20crowded%20terminals%20while%20eating%20overpriced%20airport%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20began%20to%20dread%20upcoming%20trips%20due%20to%20the%20inevitable%20layovers%20required%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20shift%20my%20travel%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-credit-cards-save-me-thousands-on-travel-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredit%20cards%20with%20travel%20rewards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20purposely%20booked%20overnight%20layovers%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20explore%20new%20destinations%2C%20and%20chose%20my%20airports%20wisely%20(some%20offer%20more%20amenities%20than%20others).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20these%20travel%20tips%2C%20I%20began%20to%20enjoy%20even%20my%20longest%20layovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPass%20the%20time%20in%20an%20airport%20lounge.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22United%20club%20in%20Dever%20with%20stool%20and%20table%20and%20chair%20seating%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11f02bfebcc4d029d9499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223829%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAirport-lounge%20access%20is%20a%20lifesaver%20when%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20lounge%20offers%20varied%20amenities%2C%20but%20most%20provide%20complimentary%20food%20and%20drinks%20along%20with%20comfortable%20seating.%20Some%20lounges%20offer%20additional%20facilities%20like%20private%20offices%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-room-airport-lounge-sleeping-qatar-airways-garden-lounge-review-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enap%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20family%20play%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20fly%20business%20class%20to%20access%20airport%20lounges%2C%20either.%20Many%20premium%20travel%20rewards%20credit%20cards%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fcapital-one-venture-x-rewards-credit-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECapital%20One%20Venture%20X%20Rewards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20provide%20lounge%20access%20to%20cardholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20i