0catch%20up%20with%20friends%20and%20family.%20I%20love%20finding%20a%20quiet%20corner%20of%20the%20airport%20to%20call%20a%20friend%20in%20London%20or%20check%20in%20with%20older%20relatives%20in%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20few%20outside%20distractions%2C%20I%20can%20be%20fully%20alert%20when%20we%20chat%2C%20and%20doing%20so%20helps%20pass%20the%20time%20while%20waiting%20for%20my%20next%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETake%20advantage%20of%20each%20airport's%20amenities.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Outdoor%20patio%20at%20Denver%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a11f04eb4be2fff9a34fc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20an%20outdoor%20patio%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Denver.%3Cp%3EJenna%20DeLaurentis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20find%20something%20interesting%20to%20do%20in%20every%20airport%20I%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-changi-airport-best-place-for-layover-australian-living-us-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChangi%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Singapore%2C%20feature%20unbelievable%20amenities%20like%20a%20swimming%20pool%20and%20yoga%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20impressed%20by%20the%20abundance%20of%20live%20music%20when%20passing%20through%20Nashville's%20airport%20and%20the%20outdoor%20patio%20at%20Denver's%20airport%20that%20allowed%20me%20to%20access%20fresh%20air%20on%20a%20long%20travel%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20search%20of%20each%20airport's%20amenities%20can%20help%20you%20find%20interesting%20things%20to%20do%2C%20whether%20you're%20passing%20through%20Istanbul%20or%20Indianapolis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20February%208%2C%202025%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20updated%20on%20April%2022%2C%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%