mlafleur.com%25252Fmdash%25252Fready-to-run-for-office%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloan%20its%20clothes%20for%20free%20to%20women%20running%20for%20public%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20for%20everything%20from%20local%20seats%20in%20town%20council%20to%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives.%20After%20their%20campaign%2C%20M.M.%20will%20donate%20the%20clothing%20to%20the%20nonprofit%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbottomlesscloset.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBottomless%20Closet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20resources%20to%20disadvantaged%20women%20working%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EM.M.LaFleur%20announced%20the%20new%20program%20on%20Presidents'%20Day%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20customers%20as%20well%20as%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Sarah%20LaFleur%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20never%20purport%20that%20clothes%20help%20move%20the%20needle%20on%20female%20representation%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20do%20our%20part%20to%20make%20things%20a%20tiny%20bit%20easier.%20As%20one%20candidate%20said%2C%20'wearing%20your%20clothes%20gave%20me%20one%20less%20thing%20to%20worry%20about%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20focus%20on%20delivering%20my%20message.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaFleur's%20company%20sent%20out%20an%20email%20the%20day%20after%20the%202016%20presidential%20election%20to%20ask%20for%20input%20on%20how%20the%20company%20could%20best%20support%20its%20community.%20Within%2048%20hours%2C%20it%20had%20received%201%2C100%20bipartisan%20replies.%20Many%20of%20them%20asked%20for%20M.M.LaFleur%20to%20support%20more%20women%20running%20for%20office%20(currently%2C%20only%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cawp.rutgers.edu%2Fcurrent-numbers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E27%25%20of%20all%20the%20elected%20offices%20in%20the%20US%20are%20held%20by%20women%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Those%20replies%20led%20to%20this%20workwear%20loaning%20program%2C%20and%20to%20an%20upcoming%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sheshouldrun.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe%20Should%20Run%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20non-partisan%20organization%20aimed%20at%20empowering%20women%20to%20run%20for%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20M.M.LaFleur's%20Ready%20to%20Run%20program%20was%20announced%2C%20other%20companies%20have%20followed%20its%20lead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20election%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126263727t3-20%26h%3Da933a0dbd89b2b53d63e2aedcd27cbbae270745e603be131012b140c4fff1f46%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f49047%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fmm-lafleur-universal-standard-free-clothes-women-running-for-office%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526amp%253Bu%253D1088116%2526amp%253Bm%253D72060%2526amp%253Burllink%253Dwww.universalstandard.com%25252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%20Standard%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20women's%20clothing%20brand%20known%20for%20its%20size-inclusive%2000-40%20range%20%E2%80%94%20will%20dress%20any%20women%20of%20any%20gender%20experience%20or%20non-binary%20person%20running%20for%20public%20office%2C%20for%20free.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222045%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2274312841_2400271903560427_2207022885543870464_o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e68108e235c180cbd7b98a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221534%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThrough%20this%20election%20year%2C%20Universal%20Standard%20%E2%80%94%20a%20women's%20clothing%20brand%20known%20for%20its%20size-inclusive%2000-40%20range%20%E2%80%94%20will%20dress%20any%20women%20of%20any%20gender%20experience%20or%20non-binary%20person%20running%20for%20public%20office%2C%20for%20free.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20standard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Twitter%2C%20Universal%20Standard%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funiversalstand%2Fstatus%2F1230272955957022720%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20anyone%20of%20any%20gender%20running%20for%20public%20office%20who%20wants%20to%20wear%20their%20clothing%20should%20reach%20out.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20everyone%20to%20help%20everyone%20dress%20and%20feel%20like%20their%20best%20selves.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20either%20program%2C%20candidates%20may%20want%20to%20check%20their%20local%20campaign%20laws%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20accepting%20the%20offer%20is%20considered%20alright%20by%20the%20fine%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20programs%20have%20drawn%20praise%20from%20women%20who%20have%20experience%20in%20public%20service.%20Rep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20(D-NY)%2C%20who%20has%20come%20under%20public%20scrutiny%20for%20everything%20from%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fentertainment%2Farchive%2F2018%2F11%2Falexandria-ocasio-cortezs-clothes-a-tedious-backlash%2F576064%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejackets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAOC%2Fstatus%2F1231280493284466688%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1231280493284466688%26ref_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.marketwatch.com%252Fstory%252Focasio-cortez-fires-back-at-the-new-york-post-after-the-paper-dragged-her-for-wearing-a-232-dress-on-the-view-2020-02-23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edresses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regrammed%20the%20news%20to%20her%20Instagram%20stories%2C%20adding%20that%20accessing%20clothes%20for%20the%20job%20while%20running%20for%20office%20was%20a%20logistical%20and%20financial%20challenge%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20candidate%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20asking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20you%20is%20helping%20them%20visualize%20you%20on%20the%20jobs.%20As%20a%20member%2C%20that%20professionalism%20helps%20you%20challenge%20subconscious%20bias.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2016%20presidential%20candidate%20Hillary%20Clinton%20also%20mentioned%20both%20company's%20lending%20programs%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHillaryClinton%2Fstatus%2F1232325832070311936%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reinforcing%20that%20%26quot%3Baffording%20professional%20clothing%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20barrier%20to%20better%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20public%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20as%20of%20March%203%2C%20M.M.LaFleur%20has%20closed%20its%20applications%20for%20new%20candidates%20after%20receiving%20over%201%2C000%20submissions%20to%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126263727t3-20%26h%3D4215fa4271b197ad66124a4a89338a9488cb87aa8e1636a2677f87416a68783d%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f49047%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fmm-lafleur-universal-standard-free-clothes-women-running-for-office%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmailto%253Areadytorun%2540mmlafleur.com%252F%5C%22%3Ereadytorun%40mmlafleur.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126263727t3-20%26h%3Da933a0dbd89b2b53d63e2aedcd27cbbae270745e603be131012b140c4fff1f46%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f49047%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fmm-lafleur-universal-standard-free-clothes-women-running-for-office%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fshar