ir%20clothes%20for%20free.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mleighton%40insider.com%20(Mara%20Leighton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fmm-lafleur-universal-standard-free-clothes-women-running-for-office%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Landscaping%20pros%20share%20the%2013%20best%20outdoor%20decor%20ideas%20that%20boost%20curb%20appeal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%2C%20gray%2C%20cement%20fountain%20is%20against%20a%20stone%20wall%20beside%20string%20lights%20that%20are%20hung%20vertically%20on%20a%20wooden%20trellis%20behind%20a%20deck.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63178108023509001aecf672%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBallard%20Designs%3B%20%D0%A2%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%87%D1%83%D0%BA%20%D0%95%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAdding%20decor%20to%20your%20outdoor%20landscape%20can%20help%20boost%20curb%20appeal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExterior%20aesthetics%20also%20make%20outdoor%20spaces%20more%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20outdoor%20decor%20ideas%20can%20help%20you%20create%20a%20beautiful%20front%20and%20backyard%20to%20be%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20talk%20about%20curb%20appeal%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20home%20value.%20But%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20selling%20your%20home%20to%20worry%20about%20outdoor%20aesthetics.%20Whether%20you're%20making%20over%20a%20front%20yard%20flower%20garden%20or%20adding%20new%20backyard%20landscaping%2C%20beautifying%20your%20yard%20can%20make%20it%20more%20enjoyable%20to%20spend%20time%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20reached%20out%20to%20two%20outdoor%20design%20experts%20to%20get%20their%20tips%20on%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20create%20a%20gorgeous%20outdoor%20landscape.%20Dave%20Angelov%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20garden%20design%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplantparenthood.design%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlant%20Parenthood%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Blythe%20Yost%20is%20the%20chief%20landscape%20architect%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56552-20%26h%3D711e9a30bc7bae678f4197afb1d4c5638ce8c86d2691d45bc7f8c9ab9b04bd36%26postID%3D63177ff1d01396438c6e1e77%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Foutdoor-decor-ideas%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftillydesign.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETilly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20online%20landscape%20design%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20creating%20a%20front%20or%20backyard%20oasis%2C%20we've%20gathered%2013%20outdoor%20decor%20ideas%20to%20boost%20your%20home's%20outdoor%20aesthetics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntegrate%20calming%20water%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Water%20runs%20over%20the%20edges%20of%20a%20cement%20pedestal%20fountain%20in%20a%20garden.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6317851f5c870800189ecebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Epeplow%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20features%20perform%20double%20duty%20in%20an%20outdoor%20setting.%20They%20provide%20a%20relaxing%2C%20audible%20water%20trickle%20and%20act%20as%20sculptural%20features.%20Angelov%20explains%20that%20a%20water%20feature%20serves%20a%20few%20purposes%20aesthetically%2C%20but%20most%20important%20is%20the%20sound.%20%26quot%3BIt%20adds%20a%20calming%20effect%20and%20turns%20an%20industrial%20space%20into%20a%20tranquil%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20fountains%20require%20an%20electrical%20hookup%2C%20so%20keep%20that%20in%20mind%20when%20selecting%20placement.%20If%20you%20live%20somewhere%20with%20freezing%20winters%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20consider%20storage%20options%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%20regarding%20winterization.%20Water%20movement%20is%20also%20essential.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20water%20isn't%20stagnant%20as%20that%20can%20attract%20mosquitoes%20to%20lay%20eggs%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20a%20steamy%20hot%20tub%20hangout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hot%20tub%20is%20sunk%20into%20a%20wood%20deck%20beside%20a%20stone%20patio%20with%20two%20lounge%20chairs.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6317870f5c870800189ecf67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EExperienceInteriors%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-inflatable-hot-tub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20tub%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20perfect%20backyard%20addition%20for%20people%20who%20love%20to%20entertain.%20Unfortunately%2C%20most%20hot%20tubs%20are%20kind%20of%20an%20eyesore.%20If%20you're%20concerned%20about%20aesthetics%2C%20consider%20choosing%20a%20bubbly%20outdoor%20tub%20made%20of%20rot-resistant%20wood%20to%20blend%20into%20the%20natural%20landscape.%20Or%20try%20jazzing%20up%20your%20new%20hangout%20spot%20with%20a%20few%20carefully%20selected%20pieces%20of%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20great%20way%20to%20integrate%20a%20hot%20tub%20into%20a%20yard%20is%20to%20sink%20it%20into%20a%20deck%20or%20add%20a%20pergola%20overhead%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20also%20add%20planters%20around%20the%20hot%20tub%20to%20mask%20the%20side.%20Remember%20to%20add%20practical%20elements%20like%20stepping%20stones%20to%20the%20tub%2C%20a%20bench%20to%20hold%20your%20towel%2C%20and%20string%20lights%20for%20evening%20dips%20to%20make%20this%20feature%20more%20usable%20and%20enjoyable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20trees%20for%20visual%20interest%20and%20privacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Small%20trees%20and%20shrubs%20border%20a%20two-story%20brown%20and%20beige%20home.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631787337e3393001879596d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EXacto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20yard%20without%20trees%20may%20be%20easy%20to%20maintain%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20feel%20bare.%20Trees%20add%20visual%20interest%20and%20can%20help%20provide%20privacy%20to%20what%20was%20once%20a%20wide-open%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20the%20right%20trees%20for%20your%20climate%20and%20space%20is%20key.%20%26quot%3BRemember%20to%20consider%20the%20mature%20size%20of%20the%20tree%20when%20selecting%20it%20for%20your%20yard%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20compact%20front%20yard%2C%20opt%20for%20bushes%20or%20dwarf-size%20trees%20that%20won't%20gobble%20up%20your%20outdoor%20real%20estate%20or%20grow%20vast%20roots%20that%20may%20damage%20nearby%20structures.%20If%20you're%20concerned%20about%20privacy%2C%20hedges%20may%20be%20an%20option%2C%20but%20consider%20that%20they%20will%20likely%20require%20regular%20maintenance.%20And%20if%20space%20or%20soil%20quality%20is%20a%20concern%2C%20choose%20statement%20planters%20for%20your%20new%20saplings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlant%20a%20gorgeous%20flower%20garden%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20flower%20bed%20with%20curved%20edges%20is%20filled%20with%20purple%2C%20blue%2C%20red%20and%20white%20flowers%2C%20ferns%20and%20shrubs%20of%20various%20heights.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6317876a5c870800189ecf8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EElenathewise%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20a%20flower%20garden%20to%20your%20outdoor%20space%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20in%20terms%20of%20aesthetics.%20A%20flower-filled%20area%20instantly%20brightens%20things%20up%20and%20makes%20a%20lifeless%20garden%20come%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20favorite%20projects%20are%20when%20clients%20say%20they%20want%20a%20more%20natural%2Fwild%20look%2C%20fewer%20straight%20lines%2C%20and%20more%20natural%20curves%20and%20organized%20randomness%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Angelov%2C%20who%20recommends%20swapping%20evergreen%20shrubs%20for%20pretty%20native%20wildflowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20your%20property%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20ways%20to%20add%20a%20touch%20of%20color%20with%20flowers%2C%20including%20planters%2C%20in-ground%20beds%2C%20and%20flower%20boxes.%20Edging%20can%20also%20help%20delineate%20a%20flower%20bed%20and%20keep%20things%20looking%20neat%20and%20tidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGo%20vertical%20with%20structures%20and%20climbing%20plants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pink%20roses%20cover%20a%20wooden%20trellis.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631787f15c870800189ecfb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERosemary%20Calvert%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20a%20touch%20of%20shade%20in%20a%20sunny%20yard%3F%20A%20trellis%20can%20help%20keep%20the%20sun%20off%20your%20face%20and%20provide%20privacy%20when%20you%20feel%20like%20hanging%20out%20outdoors.%20It's%20also%20a%20great%20way%20to%20incorporate%20plant%20life%20if%20you're%20short%20on%20ground%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20selecting%20plants%20for%20a%20trellis%2C%20consider%20companion%20planting%20to%20allow%20for%20multiple%20bloom%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%20%26quot%3BA%20classic%20example%20is%20the%20New%20Dawn%20rose%20paired%20with%20a%20Jackmanii%20clematis.%20The%20rose%20provides%20a%20woody%20structure%20that%20the%20clematis%20can%20climb%2C%20and%20each%20will%20bloom%20in%20the%20same%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20the%20right%20lighting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22String%20lights%20are%20hung%20vertically%20on%20a%20wooden%20trellis%20behind%20a%20deck.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788147e339300187959e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%D0%A2%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%87%D1%83%D0%BA%20%D0%95%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B0%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutdoor%20lights%20aren't%20just%20for%20the%20holidays%20anymore.%20They%20can%20help%20brighten%20up%20your%20yard%2C%20make%20it%20safer%2C%20and%20create%20the%20perfect%20atmosphere%20for%20outdoor%20get-togethers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLights%20add%20another%2012%20hours%20of%20decor%20to%20your%20house%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Angelov.%20He%20recommends%20adding%20uplights%20(lights%20pointing%20upward)%20to%20medium-size%20trees%20and%20around%20the%20house.%20For%20pathways%2C%20he%20says%2C%20pick%20lights%20that%20point%20down%20to%20light%20the%20way.%20Some%20decor%20pieces%20also%20feature%20built-in%20lighting%2C%20like%20fountains%20or%20other%20water%20features.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20add%20lighting%20to%20other%20spots%20in%20your%20yard%2C%20like%20around%20an%20umbrella%2C%20hanging%20from%20a%20pergola%2C%20or%20right%20in%20your%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncorporate%20a%20sculptural%20focal%20point%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20cement%20patina%20sphere%20sculptures%20sit%20on%20a%20stone%20wall%20in%20front%20of%20a%20lawn.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788335c870800189ecfe6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWayfair%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20think%20of%20sculptures%2C%20your%20mind%20probably%20goes%20to%20indoor%20spaces.%20But%20a%20sculptural%20piece%20can%20be%20an%20incredible%20focal%20point%20for%20your%20front%20or%20backyard%20garden.%20Plenty%20of%20options%20blend%20in%20well%20with%20different%20aesthetics%2C%20from%20modern%20Zen%20gardens%20to%20romantic%20English-style%20landscapes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSculptures%20can%20make%20a%20space%20feel%20really%20special%20when%20chosen%20correctly%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20align%20them%20with%20views%20from%20your%20windows%20so%20you%20can%20enjoy%20them%20or%20so%20that%20they%20draw%20you%20out%20into%20the%20landscape.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20can%20tuck%20them%20away%20so%20that%20they%20become%20surprises%20in%20your%20space%2C%20an%20exciting%20and%20unexpected%20moment%20in%20your%20backyard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsider%20succulents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rock%20garden%20planted%20with%20large%20succulents%20line%20a%20blue%20fence.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788595c870800189ecff2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKesinee%20Khaikaew%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrought%20is%20a%20common%20issue%20for%20gardeners%20throughout%20the%20US%2C%20and%20people%20are%20more%20concerned%20than%20ever%20about%20conserving%20water%20and%20choosing%20plants%20that%20don't%20require%20gallons%20of%20it%20to%20survive.%20Consider%20a%20rock%20garden%20filled%20with%20drought-tolerant%20succulents%20if%20you're%20interested%20in%20reducing%20water%20usage%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20much%20time%20watering.%20Bonus%3A%20Many%20succulents%20spread%20easily%20and%20create%20a%20gorgeous%20carpet%20of%20greenery%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20rocks%20look%20great%2C%20Angelov%20says%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20put%20down%20weed%20fabric%20to%20keep%20weeds%20at%20bay%20since%20they'll%20quickly%20crop%20up%20among%20rocks%20without%20any%20kind%20of%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESet%20the%20scene%20with%20outdoor%20furniture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wicker%20sofa%20with%20yellow%20cushions%20and%20a%20woven%20rope%20chair%20are%20positioned%20around%20a%20large%20round%20ottoman%20on%20a%20deck.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788827e339300187959fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatarzynaBialasiewicz%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20outdoor%20furniture%20is%20another%20way%20to%20increase%20the%20visual%20appeal%20of%20an%20outdoor%20space%20for%20those%20who%20prefer%20not%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20dirty.%20Creating%20a%20comfortable%20place%20to%20sit%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20enjoy%20the%20outdoors%20and%20entertain%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20outdoor%20furniture%20for%20your%20garden%20or%20patio%20can%20really%20add%20the%20finishing%20touches%20to%20your%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%20%26quot%3BA%20great%20wicker%20sofa%20can%20quickly%20create%20a%20beachy%20vibe%2C%20or%20a%20bold-colored%20bistro%20table%20can%20be%20the%20perfect%20set%20for%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20cottage-style%20garden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20keep%20climate%20in%20mind%20when%20selecting%20furniture.%20Yost%20says%20recycled%20plastic%20works%20well%20for%20rainy%20and%20humid%20clients%20and%20cautions%20that%20metal%20is%20susceptible%20to%20water%20damage%20and%20can%20get%20very%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHang%20a%20wreath%20on%20the%20front%20door%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20beige%2C%20yellow%2C%20and%20orange%20wheat%20and%20grass%20wreath%20hangs%20from%20a%20black%20door.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788d15c870800189ed009%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETriggerPhoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecor%20to%20boost%20curb%20appeal%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20complicated%20or%20pricey.%20Adding%20a%20simple%20wreath%20to%20your%20front%20door%20can%20make%20your%20entryway%20look%20more%20put%20together.%20You%20might%20even%20try%20changing%20wreaths%20seasonally%20or%20according%20to%20upcoming%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYost%20says%20she's%20especially%20fond%20of%20DIY%20wreaths.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20easiest%20to%20start%20with%20a%20wire%20frame%20and%20then%20use%20young%20boughs%20and%20branches%20to%20build%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BStick%20in%20anything%20you%20find%20in%20your%20garden%20like%20seed%20pods%2C%20leaves%2C%20flowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlant%20an%20herb%20garden%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20pots%20of%20herbs%20are%20in%20front%20of%20low%20raised%20garden%20beds%20containing%20a%20variety%20of%20herbs.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631788f97e33930018795a0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPaulMaguire%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlowers%20are%20beautiful%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20aren't%20edible.%20If%20you're%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20foodie%2C%20consider%20planting%20a%20fragrant%2C%20mouth-watering%20herb%20garden%20that%20you%20can%20harvest%20from%20as%20needed.%20Herbs%20like%20mint%20and%20thyme%20are%20low%20maintenance%20and%20attract%20pollinators%20like%20butterflies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20an%20herb%20garden%20effectively%20reduces%20lawn%2C%20which%20Angelov%20points%20out%20is%20a%20huge%20waste%20of%20water.%20%26quot%3BThink%20of%20your%20garden%20as%20a%20long-term%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20paper%20you%20hand%20in%20and%20never%20read%20again.%20It's%20a%20live%20ecosystem%20that%20constantly%20needs%20to%20be%20nurtured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20a%20weatherproof%20rug%20to%20your%20patio%20or%20deck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chairs%20are%20gathered%20around%20a%20black%20and%20white%20diamond%20print%20rug%20on%20a%20deck.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6317891d5c870800189ed02f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArranging%20a%20rug%20underneath%20your%20outdoor%20dining%20or%20lounge%20set%20is%20the%20perfect%20way%20to%20add%20a%20burst%20of%20color.%20Placing%20a%20rug%20also%20makes%20a%20space%20feel%20more%20cohesive%20and%20ties%20the%20whole%20%26quot%3Broom%26quot%3B%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20the%20rug%20you%20purchase%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20for%20outdoor%20use%20because%20outdoor%20rugs%20must%20withstand%20the%20elements%2C%20heavy%20foot%20traffic%2C%20and%20be%20able%20to%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yost.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20about%20outdoor%20rugs%20is%20it's%20a%20great%20place%20to%20have%20a%20little%20fun!%20You%20may%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20take%20a%20risk%20with%20an%20indoor%20rug%20that%20you%20see%20every%20day%2C%20but%20a%20great%20pop%20of%20color%20or%20bold%20print%20outside%20might%20be%20just%20the%20right%20option%20for%20an%20evening%20or%20weekend%20relaxing%20outdoors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EApply%20a%20fresh%20coat%20of%20paint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20porch%20of%20a%20beige%20colored%20home%20is%20shown%20and%20the%20front%20door%20is%20black.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631789725c870800189ed047%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESherwin-Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20indoors%20or%20out%2C%20sometimes%20all%20you%20need%20is%20a%20fresh%20coat%20of%20paint%20to%20beautify%20a%20space%20and%20breathe%20some%20life%20into%20it%20again.%20Consider%20repainting%20your%20front%20door%20or%20window%20trim%20to%20give%20your%20home's%20exterior%20a%20quick%20facelift.%20And%20if%20you're%20feeling%20adventurous%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20bold%20color%20choice%20like%20dramatic%20black%2C%20cheery%20yellow%2C%20or%20vibrant%20red.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYost%20says%20there's%20been%20an%20uptick%20in%20interest%20for%20neutral%20paint%20colors%20with%20blue%20and%20green%20undertones.%20Some%20favorites%20include%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56552-20%26h%3D03ca5ff06e3bb431c20ee82fa0a4b9c4ca74247907870a93fc1da913f32218d6%26postID%3D63177ff1d01396438c6e1e77%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Foutdoor-decor-ideas%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.benjaminmoore.com%252Fen-us%252Fpaint-colors%252Fcolor%252F2126-20%252Fraccoon-fur%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaccoon%20Fur%20by%20Benjamin%20Moore%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sherwin-williams.com%2Fhomeowners%2Fcolor%2Ffind-and-explore-colors%2Fpaint-colors-by-family%2FSW7046-anonymous%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnonymous%20by%20Sherwin%20Williams%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20like%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Foutdoor-decor-ideas%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776868929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63178108023509001aecf672%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Foutdoor-decor-ideas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20you're%20looking%20to%20boost%20your%20curb%20appeal%20or%20just%20enjoy%20your%20home's%20exterior%20spaces%2C%20these%20outdoor%20decor%20ideas%20come%20recommended%20by%20pros.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22stephcoelhowrites%40gmail.com%20(Steph%20Coelho)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Foutdoor-decor-ideas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20to%20buy%20postage%20stamps%2C%20including%20the%20post%20office%2C%20online%2C%20ATMs%2C%20and%20grocery%20stores%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22usps%20postage%20stamps%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f96f624f21803001222bf37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPostage%20stamps%20are%20handy%20when%20you%20need%20to%20send%20greeting%20cards%2C%20invoices%2C%20or%20other%20physical%20mail.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELocal%20post%20offices%20carry%20them%2C%20or%20you%20can%20order%20them%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.usps.com%2Fstore%2Fresults%2Fstamps%2F_%2FN-9y93lv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Postal%20Service's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrocery%20stores%2C%20pharmacies%2C%20and%20similar%20retailers%20often%20carry%20booklets%20of%20stamps%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20want%20to%20send%20a%20greeting%20or%20holiday%20card%2C%20mail%20in%20an%20absentee%20ballot%2C%20pay%20a%20bill%2C%20or%20connect%20with%20some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoronavirus-snail-mail-letters-better-than-zoom-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equarantine%20pen%20pals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20always%20useful%20to%20have%20some%20stamps%20on%20hand.%20It%20costs%2060%20cents%20to%20send%20a%20domestic%201-ounce%2C%20standard-sized%20envelope%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usps.com%2Fbusiness%2Fprices.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Postal%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20an%20affordable%20way%20to%20correspond%20with%20people%20in%20a%20tactile%2C%20memorable%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20booklet%20of%2020%20stamps%20comes%20out%20to%20around%20%2412.%20The%20beauty%20of%20%26quot%3Bforever%26quot%3B%20stamps%20is%20that%20you%20can%20still%20use%20them%20even%20when%20the%20price%20of%20mailing%20a%20letter%20goes%20up.%20If%20you%20find%20a%20roll%20of%20forever%20stamps%20from%202016%2C%20when%20the%20price%20was%2047%20cents%2C%20you%20can%20still%20stick%20one%20on%20an%20envelope%20today%20and%20drop%20it%20into%20a%20mailbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20places%20you%20can%20pick%20up%20stamps%2C%20not%20just%20at%20the%20local%20post%20office.%20If%20you're%20in%20need%20of%20postage%2C%20here%20are%20the%20ways%20you%20can%20buy%20stamps.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EYour%20local%20post%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Post%20office%20self-service%20kiosk%20in%20New%20York%20City%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f962856f21803001222bd7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20self-service%20kiosk%20at%20a%20post%20office%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ELes%20Shu%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20given%2C%20but%20depending%20on%20the%20time%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20customer%20service%20queue%20can%20get%20long.%20If%20you%20just%20need%20stamps%2C%20use%20one%20of%20the%20electronic%20self-service%20kiosks%20(where%20available)%20instead%3B%20there%20are%20usually%20no%20lines%20to%20use%20them.%20The%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20specialty%20stamps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUSPS.com%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221105%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20stamps%20page%20of%20the%20USPS%20website%20depicting%20holiday%20stamps%20for%202022%2C%20which%20are%20priced%20at%20%2412%20for%20a%20book%20of%2020.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63879198d346c1001894917c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUSPS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.usps.com%2Fstore%2Fresults%2Fstamps%2F_%2FN-9y93lv%3F_requestid%3D42317%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20office's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20variety%20of%20stamps%2C%20from%20the%20standard%20US%20Flag%20to%20seasonal%20(e.g.%2C%20Christmas%2C%20Diwali%2C%20Kwanzaa%2C%20Halloween)%20and%20themed%20options%20(e.g.%2C%20Peanuts%20characters%2C%20the%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20images%2C%20elephants)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20notable%20Americans%20like%20Edmonia%20Lewis%2C%20Eugenie%20Clark%2C%20Chien-Shiung%20Wu%2C%20and%20Pete%20Seeger.%20The%20site%20lets%20you%20filter%20by%20color%2C%20shape%2C%20theme%2C%20denomination%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ERetailers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20from%20grocery%20stores%20to%20pharmacies%20to%20office%20supply%20stores%20often%20sell%20stamps.%20Instead%20of%20just%20chancing%20whether%20your%20local%20Publix%20or%20Kroger%20has%20them%2C%20you%20can%20find%20out%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftools.usps.com%2Ffind-location.htm%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%